{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1772236304,"nonce":"fFBvZn7/LiFjZghX3hiAn5M6D58=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87unfeB","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/322","origin":"github"},"title":"gather-project-knowledge: extend validation to cover summary statistics","message":"## Summary\n\nThe `gather-project-knowledge` skill's validation step (step 4 in SKILL.md) checks\nthat package names in profiles match `\u003cname\u003e` elements in `package.xml`. However, it\ndoes not validate summary statistics — repo counts, package counts per layer, and\ntotals in `workspace_overview.md`.\n\nThe second run of the skill ([unh_marine_autonomy#96](https://github.com/rolker/unh_marine_autonomy/pull/96))\nproduced correct package names (34/34 profiles validated) but had wrong counts in the\nLayer Structure summary table:\n\n| Layer | Claimed | Actual |\n|---|---|---|\n| underlay repos | 8 | 9 |\n| underlay packages | 20 | 22 |\n| platforms packages | 10 | 9 |\n| sensors packages | 11 | 10 |\n\n## Root Cause\n\nSame class of bug as [#320](https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/320):\nsummary statistics were copied from an intermediate agent output instead of being\nderived by counting the validated inventory table. The fix for #320 addressed package\nnames but not numeric summaries.\n\n## Proposed Fix\n\nTwo changes to `.claude/skills/gather-project-knowledge/SKILL.md`:\n\n1. **Step 3 (Generate summaries)**: Add instruction that all counts in\n   `workspace_overview.md` (repos per layer, packages per layer, totals) must be\n   derived by counting entries in the structured inventory table from step 2 — never\n   from pre-computed summaries or intermediate outputs.\n\n2. **Step 4 (Validate)**: Extend validation to check that summary counts in\n   `workspace_overview.md` match the Package Inventory table. For each layer, count\n   the repos and packages listed in the inventory and compare against the Layer\n   Structure table.\n\n## Context\n\n- Skill definition: `.claude/skills/gather-project-knowledge/SKILL.md`\n- Original fidelity fix: [#320](https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/320)\n- Run where this was caught: [unh_marine_autonomy#96](https://github.com/rolker/unh_marine_autonomy/pull/96)\n  (counts fixed in follow-up commit)\n\n---\n**Authored-By**: `Claude Code Agent`\n**Model**: `Claude Opus 4.6`","files":null}]}